                    <span>Once I started reading this book I realized how much thought has to go into the retirement proccess. This book starts you off in the right place and takes you through the proccess in exactly the right order. I found the  book very easy to comprehend and the charts were very helpfull to  illustrate the points that were being made. I have read other books on the  subject of retirement and I found that this book is very comprehensive and  easy to follow.</span>
                  
